MSI has announced that a selection of its latest gaming laptops will be discounted on Black Friday in South Africa. These specials will run for one day only on Friday 23 November and will be available from retailers including Takealot and Incredible Connection. Many laptops have been discounted by 20% or more, and the selection of devices on sale feature impressive specifications. All the gaming laptops on special boast Intel 8th-generation processors along with Nvidia GeForce GTX graphics cards, delivering great performance in a portable form factor. Below are the MSI gaming laptops which will be discounted on Black Friday, along with their pricing and specifications.    